<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Marodack</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-10-17 09:27:02</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I was lucky enough to get one in CoM.  It dropped off a skel. Since then I have yet to see anyone else get this staff. From what I understand its very rare. What I mean by very rare is, you may see one or 2 peeps with this staff on your server. <BR>
<BR>
I'll say this much about the staff. IT SAVES LIVES!!! This staff is very important in group when you run out of mana. I no longer have to save mana to evac.  As long as I'm not getting beat on I can use it.  Its casting time is the same as the regular port spell.  <BR>
<BR>
Another nice use is when meding and some lame wolf or low lvl skel comes along and decides to hit you, you can get up and smack the hell out of it.  I hit for 23's, killing lame low lvl pests fast rather than wasting my mana.<BR>
<BR>
This staff by no means is a waste. Even though a wiz gets portal to nek, you can see the real value of it when mana is gone.  I will never sell this staff and have been offered tons of stuff for it.<BR>
<BR>
If you get lucky enough to loot it and your a wiz keep it.. do not sell this item because one day will come when you will be glad you have it.  And if your in a group and your a wiz I hope your group plays need before greed. Its the only way to play.<BR>
<BR>
Marodack Evillore<BR>
52 DE wizy on bristlebane</font></td></tr></table>
